NetCDF iCommands distro package instructions

Requires irods-icommands-4.1.10 to be installed. These instructions will assume
this package is already installed.

Requires irods-runtime-4.1.10 to be installed (downloads page)

CentOS 6

    sudo yum install irods-runtime-4.1.10-centos6-x86_64.rpm \
                     irods-api-plugin-netcdf-1.0-centos6.rpm \
                     irods-icommands-netcdf-1.0-centos6.rpm

CentOS 7

    sudo yum install irods-runtime-4.1.10-centos7-x86_64.rpm \
                     irods-api-plugin-netcdf-1.0-centos7.rpm \
                     irods-icommands-netcdf-1.0-centos7.rpm

Ubuntu 14
Requires libcurl4-gnutls-dev to be installed as well

    sudo apt-get install libcurl4-gnutls-dev
    sudo dpkg -i irods-runtime-4.1.10-ubuntu14-x86_64.deb \
                 irods-api-plugin-netcdf-1.0-ubuntu14.deb \
                 irods-icommands-netcdf-1.0-ubuntu14.deb
    sudo apt-get -f install
